                <p class="p1"><em>If it’s hand dyed?</em></p>
                <p class="p1">Our hand dyed and Shibori fabrics are pre-washed and tumble-dried low after dyeing. Repeated washing or prolonged exposure to direct sunlight may cause colors to fade slightly. The plain linen on the reverse of the pillow has not been pre-washed, so we suggest hand washing in cold water and hanging to dry as otherwise there may be shrinkage with the appliqué on the reverse.</p>
                <p class="p1">Iron on medium heat as necessary. If your pillow has a metallic back, please see below.</p>
